### Mehedi Portfolio API Tests
### Install "REST Client" extension to run these

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

###
# GET all projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Accept: application/json

###
# GET a single project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Accept: application/json

###
# GET all skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills
Accept: application/json

###
# POST contact message
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Recruiter",
  "email": "john@company.com",
  "message": "Hi Mehedi! We have an exciting remote position for you. Would love to connect."
}

###
# POST contact - validation test (missing fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "message": "short"
}
